---
title: "Evercooked Newsletters: Recipes, Stories, and Traditions"
description: Explore a collection of heartfelt stories, vibrant recipes, and rich traditions shared through our weekly newsletters. Join the Evercooked community and discover the memories behind the dishes that bring us together.
layout: split
full_image: /images/og.png
apple_touch_image: /images/apple-touch.png
---

<div class="w-full px-2 sm:px-3 py-6 lg:py-4 lg:bg-[#eaeaef] mt-3 lg:pb-0 lg:mt-0">
	<div class="lg:bg-[#eaeaef] lg:py-3">
		<div class=" lg:mb-3 lg:rounded-sm">
			<h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium my-0 alt_font tracking-wide mb-4 text-center">Newsletters</h1>
		</div>
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 lg:gap-3">
			<% blog('newsletters').articles.select(&:published?).each do |article| %>
				<div class="h-full p-4 bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition text-body flex flex-col justify-between hover:text-body hover:cursor-pointer">
					<a href="<%= article.url.chomp('/') %>" class="block">
						<img src="<%= article.data.featured_image %>" alt="<%= article.title %>" class="w-full h-56 object-cover rounded-lg">
					</a>
					<a href="<%= article.url.chomp('/') %>" class="block my-3 text-xl font-semibold leading-tight hover:no-underline text-body">
						<%= article.title %>
					</a>
					<%= article.summary(150, '...') %>
					<div class="mt-auto">
						<a href="<%= article.url.chomp('/') %>" class="text-link hover:text-linkhover inline-block">Read more â†’</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			<% end %>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
